{"tid":1284462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛孟靜：建制派倡另覓地方開會處理民生項目是偽善","createTime":"2019-07-04T07:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T08:00:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"741cf1518286ca2de3f25b489a02804ac4ab1d28","tid":1284462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:34:51.000Z","msg":"議會陣線議員毛孟靜表示，財委會主席陳健波已經表明，未來兩星期不會開財會，但現在建制派議員又說可考慮另覓地方再會處理民生項目，她形容是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偽善</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜認為，建制派議員根本不想開財會，只是想「裝出姿勢」通過民生項目，她質疑如有能開財會，代表可以開到立法會大會，她認為建制派不希望行政長官林鄭月娥出席答問、傳召鄭若驊及討論不信任動議等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於有建議提出沒爭議的項目可考慮以書面傳閱通過，毛孟靜認為是非常危險和不能接受，因為會立下先例。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466602-20190704.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466602-20190704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=b988e89c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466602-20190704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b890596a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466602-20190704.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d425292acf640c7b0879b15cb7e5b36e7aa95c2b","tid":1284462,"uid":78574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"書面傳閱通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b096d43f75a1823b01237f11871f23645ca4dec","tid":1284462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d425292acf640c7b0879b15cb7e5b36e7aa95c2b","tid":1284462,"uid":78574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"書面傳閱通過<img src